response.overview: May 14th, 2011 :: Combat Zone Wrestling presents Proving Grounds from the Asylum Arena in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, USA. Matches include:  • Alex Colon vs. Rich Swann  • Ty Hagen vs. Ryan Eagles  • AKUMA vs. Jonathan Gresham  • Jake Crist vs. Ryan McBride  • Dog Collar Match Drake Younger vs. Scotty Vortekz  • Masada vs. Sami Callihan  • Ultraviolent Underground Title Match Danny Havoc (c) vs. Ryan Slater (w/Joe Gacy)  • Home Run Derby Death Match Danny Havoc & tHURTeen vs. The Runaways (Joe Gacy & Ryan Slater)  • CZW World Heavyweight Title Match Devon Moore (c) vs. Robert Anthony  • CZW Tag Team Title Match The Briscoes (Jay Briscoe & Mark Briscoe) (c) vs. The Nigerian Nightmares (Maifu & Saifu)  • CZW Junior Heavyweight Title Match Adam Cole (c) vs. AR Fox
response.title: CZW Proving Grounds 2011
